org.batfish.datamodel

Class IntegerSpace

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.batfish.datamodel.IntegerSpace

  • @ParametersAreNonnullByDefault
public final class IntegerSpace
extends Object
    A finite, closed, not necessarily contiguous space of integers. Designed to be able to represent set of port ranges or other packet fields that are integers. Integer spaces are by design immutable, but can be altered by converting toBuilder() and recreated again.
